LGU 1

year: 2004
tax due: 100

Annual mode: 100
	   Jan: (-10%) 100 - 10 = 90

Qtry mode: 25 / Qtr
	Qtr 1 (Jan - Mar): 
		on or before march 30	: (-10%) 25 - 2.50 = 22.50
	Qtr 2 (Apr - Jun): 
		on or before June 30	: (-10%) 25 - 2.50 = 22.50
		:
		:


	Qtr 1 (Jan - Mar): 
		after march 30, april 15	: (+2% per each month overdue) 25 + 2 = 27
	Qtr 2 (Apr - Jun): 
		on or before June 30	: (-10%) 25 - 2.50 = 22.50
		after June 30, July 1	: (+2% per each month overdue) 25 + 2 = 27

if missed whole of 2004:
	pay on Jan 2005: 100 + %24 = 124


