LGU 2

year: 2004
tax due: 100

Annual mode: 100
	   Jan: (-10%) 100 - 10 = 90

Qtry mode: 25 / Qtr
	Qtr 1 (Jan - Mar): 
		on or before march 30	: (-10%) 25 - 2.50 = 22.50
	Qtr 2 (Apr - Jun): 
		on or before June 30	: (-10%) 25 - 2.50 = 22.50
		:
		:


	Qtr 1 (Jan - Mar): 
		after march 30, april 15	: (+2% per each month overdue) 25 + 2 = 27
	Qtr 2 (Apr - Jun): 
		on Apr: (+2% per each month start Apr) 25 + 0.5 = 25.50
		on May: (+2% per each month start Apr) 25 + 1 = 26.00
		on Jun: (+2% per each month start Apr) 25 + 1.5 = 26.50
		
		on Apr, will pay for Q2-Q4: 75 + 1.50 = 76.50
		on May, will pay for Q2-Q4: 75 + 3.00 = 78.00
				
	Qtr 3 (Jul - Sep):
		on Apr: (+2% per each month start Apr) 25 + 0.5 = 25.50

		
